{
    "poem_title": "À M. ALPHONSE DE LAMARTINE",
    "author": "Marceline Desbordes-Valmore",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1830",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Triste et morne sur le rivage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Où l’espoir oublia mes jours,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "J’enviais à l’oiseau sauvage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Les cris qu’il pousse dans l’orage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Et que je renferme toujours !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Triste et morne sur le rivage\nOù l’espoir oublia mes jours,\nJ’enviais à l’oiseau sauvage\nLes cris qu’il pousse dans l’orage\nEt que je renferme toujours !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Et quand l’eau s’enfuyait, semée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "De tant d’heures, de tant de mois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sous ma voile sombre et fermée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "D’une vie autrefois aimée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Je ne traînais plus que le poids !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et quand l’eau s’enfuyait, semée\nDe tant d’heures, de tant de mois,\nSous ma voile sombre et fermée,\nD’une vie autrefois aimée\nJe ne traînais plus que le poids !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "J’osais, au fond de ma misère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Rêvant sous mes genoux pliés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Sans haleine pour ma prière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Murmurer à Dieu : « Dieu, mon père !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Mon père ! vous nous oubliez !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’osais, au fond de ma misère,\nRêvant sous mes genoux pliés,\nSans haleine pour ma prière,\nMurmurer à Dieu : « Dieu, mon père !\nMon père ! vous nous oubliez !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "« Vous ne donnez repos ni trêve,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Ni calme à notre errant esquif",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Tantôt échoué sur la grève,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Tantôt emporté comme un rêve,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Perdu dans l’orage ou captif !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Vous ne donnez repos ni trêve,\nNi calme à notre errant esquif\nTantôt échoué sur la grève,\nTantôt emporté comme un rêve,\nPerdu dans l’orage ou captif !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "« Partout où le malheur l’égare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Une mère a peur de mourir ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "J’ai peur : j’ose nommer barbare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Le destin mobile et bizarre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Qui fit mes enfants pour souffrir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Partout où le malheur l’égare,\nUne mère a peur de mourir ;\nJ’ai peur : j’ose nommer barbare\nLe destin mobile et bizarre\nQui fit mes enfants pour souffrir !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "« Qui prendra la rame affligée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Quand la barque, sans mouvement,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "De mon faible poids allégée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Leur paraîtra vide, changée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Et sur un plus morne élément ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Qui prendra la rame affligée,\nQuand la barque, sans mouvement,\nDe mon faible poids allégée,\nLeur paraîtra vide, changée,\nEt sur un plus morne élément ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "« Sans char, sans prêtre, au cimetière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Leur piété me conduira ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Puis, d’un peu de buis ou de lierre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Doux monument de sa prière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Le plus tendre me couvrira !… »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Sans char, sans prêtre, au cimetière\nLeur piété me conduira ;\nPuis, d’un peu de buis ou de lierre,\nDoux monument de sa prière,\nLe plus tendre me couvrira !… »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Tout passe ! Et je vis disparaître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "L’orage avec l’oiseau plongeur ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Et sur mon étroite fenêtre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "La lune qui venait de naître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Répandit sa douce blancheur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout passe ! Et je vis disparaître\nL’orage avec l’oiseau plongeur ;\nEt sur mon étroite fenêtre\nLa lune qui venait de naître\nRépandit sa douce blancheur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "J’étendis mes bras devant elle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Comme pour atteindre un ami",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Dont le pas vivant et fidèle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Tout à coup au cœur se révèle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Sur le seuil longtemps endormi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’étendis mes bras devant elle,\nComme pour atteindre un ami\nDont le pas vivant et fidèle\nTout à coup au cœur se révèle\nSur le seuil longtemps endormi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Je ne sais quelle voix puissante",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Retint mon souffle suspendu ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Voix d’en haut, brise ravissante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Qui me relevait languissante,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Comme si Dieu m’eût répondu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je ne sais quelle voix puissante\nRetint mon souffle suspendu ;\nVoix d’en haut, brise ravissante,\nQui me relevait languissante,\nComme si Dieu m’eût répondu !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Mais par trop d’espoir affaiblie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et voilant mes pleurs sous ma main,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "J’ai dit dans ma mélancolie :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "« Lorsque tout m’ignore ou m’oublie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Quel ange est donc sur mon chemin ? »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais par trop d’espoir affaiblie,\nEt voilant mes pleurs sous ma main,\nJ’ai dit dans ma mélancolie :\n« Lorsque tout m’ignore ou m’oublie,\nQuel ange est donc sur mon chemin ? »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "C’était vous ! J’entendis des ailes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Battre au milieu d’un ciel plus doux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Et sur le sentier d’étincelles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Que formaient d’ardentes parcelles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "L’ange qui venait, c’était vous !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’était vous ! J’entendis des ailes\nBattre au milieu d’un ciel plus doux ;\nEt sur le sentier d’étincelles\nQue formaient d’ardentes parcelles,\nL’ange qui venait, c’était vous !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Oui, du haut de son vol sublime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Lamartine jetait mon nom,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Comme d’une invisible cime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "À la barque, au bord de l’abîme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Le ciel ému jette un rayon !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oui, du haut de son vol sublime,\nLamartine jetait mon nom,\nComme d’une invisible cime,\nÀ la barque, au bord de l’abîme,\nLe ciel ému jette un rayon !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Doux comme une voix qui pardonne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Depuis que ton souffle a passé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Sur mon front pâle et sans couronne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Une sainte pitié résonne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Autour de mon sort délaissé !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Doux comme une voix qui pardonne,\nDepuis que ton souffle a passé\nSur mon front pâle et sans couronne,\nUne sainte pitié résonne\nAutour de mon sort délaissé !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Jamais, dans son errante alarme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "La Péri, pour porter aux cieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Ne puisa de plus humble larme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Que le pleur plein d’un triste charme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Dont tes chants ont mouillé mes yeux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Jamais, dans son errante alarme,\nLa Péri, pour porter aux cieux,\nNe puisa de plus humble larme\nQue le pleur plein d’un triste charme\nDont tes chants ont mouillé mes yeux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Mais dans ces chants que ma mémoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Et mon cœur s’apprennent tout bas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Doux à lire, plus doux à croire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! n’as-tu pas dit le mot gloire ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Et ce mot, je ne l’entends pas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais dans ces chants que ma mémoire\nEt mon cœur s’apprennent tout bas,\nDoux à lire, plus doux à croire,\nOh ! n’as-tu pas dit le mot gloire ?\nEt ce mot, je ne l’entends pas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 17,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Car je suis une faible femme ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Je n’ai su qu’aimer et souffrir ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "Ma pauvre lyre, c’est mon âme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Et toi seul découvres la flamme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "D’une lampe qui va mourir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car je suis une faible femme ;\nJe n’ai su qu’aimer et souffrir ;\nMa pauvre lyre, c’est mon âme,\nEt toi seul découvres la flamme\nD’une lampe qui va mourir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 18,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Devant tes hymnes de poète,",
